tool_description:
Cricket live score service at CricketApi allows you to follow real time cricket results, standings and fixtures. Live matches from cricket leagues has ball by ball coverage for every inning and detailed tables for fall of the wicket and partnership.
If you find problems,subscribing, please try at: https://rapidapi.com/fluis.lacasse/api/cricketapi12
For increased rates and more sports, please look at: https://rapidapi.com/fluis.lacasse/api/allsportsapi2/
name: CricketAPI2
title: CricketAPI2

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: Search cricket players, teams, and tournaments using a search term.

required_parameters.name: term
required_parameters.description: The search term to find cricket-related entities.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com/api/cricket/search/kabul"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cricketapi21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
